des: "This is an easy dressing to make that is great over fruit. Just put it in a jar, shake, and it's ready to go.  A little goes a long way, and really enhances most fruits, especially oranges, grapes and apples."
ins: In a jar, combine oil, honey, vinegar, poppy seeds, sesame seeds, paprika, and Worcestershire sauce. Place lid tightly on jar, and shake until dressing is blended.
